<h1>Hi <%=@invitee.firstname %>,</h1>
<pre>
You will probably be glad to know that <%=@inviter.name %> has recommended you to the Roooster community of design professionals, by adding you to our directory of trusted creatives. 

You are invited to join us and <%= link_to "create your profile", accept_invitation_url(@resource, :invitation_token => @token) %> or to have a look at Roooster. 

If you have any questions about Roooster, you are most welcome to contact us at info@roooster.net. You may find answers to specific questions on our FAQ page: https://roooster.net/faq.  

Looking forward to having you with us,
The Roooster team
